204
00:16:37,916 --> 00:16:41,628
Aku tak peduli dari mana asal uang itu.

205
00:16:42,128 --> 00:16:44,547
Aku hanya ingin menunjukkan
ke wajah sombong mereka.

206
00:16:45,507 --> 00:16:47,258
Jika kami perlu menghubungimu,

207
00:16:48,009 --> 00:16:49,594
kami akan menghubungi lewat ini.

208
00:16:51,888 --> 00:16:52,889
Tetap dekat.

209
00:16:55,475 --> 00:16:56,810
Makin buruk dari sini.

210
00:16:57,852 --> 00:16:59,229
Aku menyelesaikan persetujuan pemindahan.

211
00:16:59,312 --> 00:17:01,231
Setiap bagian kuningan dipoles,

212
00:17:01,314 --> 00:17:04,734
